
= SDL_BlendMode =
An enumeration of blend modes used in [[SDL_RenderCopy]]() and drawing operations.


== Values ==
{|
|SDL_BLENDMODE_NONE
|no blending
|-
| 
|dstRGBA = srcRGBA
|-
|SDL_BLENDMODE_BLEND
|alpha blending
|-
| 
|dstRGB = (srcRGB * srcA) + (dstRGB * (1-srcA))
|-
| 
|dstA = srcA + (dstA * (1-srcA))
|-
|SDL_BLENDMODE_ADD
|additive blending
|-
| 
|dstRGB = (srcRGB * srcA) + dstRGB
|-
| 
|dstA = dstA
|-
|SDL_BLENDMODE_MOD
|color modulate
|-
| 
|dstRGB = srcRGB * dstRGB
|-
| 
|dstA = dstA
|}
